{"data":[{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"1","text":"Zvirokwazvo ruoko rwaJehovha haruna kupfupika kuti rukonewe kuponesa,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"2","text":"Asi zvakaipa zvenyu zvakakuparadzanisai"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"3","text":"Nokuti maoko enyu akasvibiswa neropa,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"4","text":"Hapana anochemera kururamisira;"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"5","text":"Vanochochonya mazai emvumbi,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"6","text":"Matandira avo haabatsiri pakupfeka;"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"7","text":"Tsoka dzavo dzinomhanyira kundopinda muchivi;"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"8","text":"Nzira yorugare havaizivi;"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"9","text":"Naizvozvo kururamisira kuri kure nesu,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"10","text":"Sebofu tinotsvanzvadzira tichitevedza madziro,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"11","text":"Tose tiri kuomba samapere;"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"12","text":"Nokuti kutadza kwedu kwawanda pamberi penyu,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"13","text":"kumukira nokunyengera Jehovha,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"14","text":"Naizvozvo kururamisirwa kwadzorerwa shure,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"15","text":"Zvokwadi haichawanikwi"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"16","text":"Akaona kuti pakanga pasina munhu,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"17","text":"Akashonga kururama sechidzitiro chechipfuva,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"18","text":"Sezvavakaita, saizvozvo acharipira"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"19","text":"Kubva kumavirira, vanhu vachatya Jehovha,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"20","text":"“Mudzikinuri achauya kuZioni,"},{"book":"Isaya","chapter":"59","verse":"21","text":"“Kana ndirini, iyi ndiyo sungano yangu navo,” ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha. “Mweya wangu uri pamusoro pako, namashoko angu andakaisa mumuromo mako hazvichabvi pamuromo wako, kana pamiromo yavana venyu, kana pamiromo yezvizvarwa zvavo kubva zvino nokusingaperi,” ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha."}]}